Docker Swarm

***For docker swarm we have to use git bash***
Check this first
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-server/virtualization/hyper-v/get-started/create-a-virtual-switch-for-hyper-v-virtual-machines
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/virtualization/hyper-v-on-windows/quick-start/enable-hyper-v

Step 1 :  Create Docker machines (to act as nodes for Docker Swarm)   
Create one machine as manager and others as workers
This machine is the manager
docker-machine create --driver hyperv manager1

Step2: To see the information of the machine run command - Will give info about manager1 machine (IP, name, location, tls verify)
docker-machine env manager1